sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant gRPC as Caikit gRPC Server<br/>8085/TCP Configurable TLS
    participant HTTP as Caikit HTTP Gateway<br/>8080/TCP Configurable TLS
    participant TextGenLocal as TextGeneration<br/>(Local)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(Remote)
    participant PeftTuning as PeftPromptTuning<br/>(Training)
    participant EmbedMod as EmbeddingModule
    participant TGISClient as TGISGenerationClient<br/>(gRPC)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>Configurable Port/TCP
    participant HFModel as HuggingFace Model<br/>(in-memory)
    participant STModel as SentenceTransformers<br/>(in-memory)
    participant Distributed as PyTorch Distributed<br/>29550/TCP plaintext
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference
    Client->>gRPC: TextGenerationTaskRequest<br/>gRPC / Configurable TLS
    gRPC->>TextGenLocal: dispatch run()
    TextGenLocal->>HFModel: generate()<br/>(CausalLM or Seq2SeqLM)
    HFModel-->>TextGenLocal: Generated tokens
    TextGenLocal-->>gRPC: GeneratedTextResult
    gRPC-->>Client: TextGenerationTaskResponse

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation (Streaming)
    Client->>gRPC: ServerStreamingTextGenerationTaskRequest<br/>gRPC / Configurable TLS
    gRPC->>TextGenTGIS: dispatch run_stream_out()
    TextGenTGIS->>TGISClient: generate_stream()
    TGISClient->>TGIS: GenerationRequest<br/>gRPC / Optional mTLS
    loop Streaming tokens
        TGIS-->>TGISClient: GenerationResponse (token)
        TGISClient-->>TextGenTGIS: yield token
        TextGenTGIS-->>gRPC: yield GeneratedTextStreamResult
        gRPC-->>Client: stream token
    end

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 3: PEFT Prompt Tuning Training
    Client->>gRPC: TrainingRequest<br/>gRPC / Configurable TLS
    gRPC->>PeftTuning: dispatch train()
    PeftTuning->>HFModel: Load base model
    opt Distributed Training
        PeftTuning->>Distributed: torchrun elastic launch<br/>29550/TCP plaintext
        Distributed-->>PeftTuning: Synchronized gradients
    end
    PeftTuning->>PeftTuning: PEFT prompt tuning<br/>(forward/backward passes)
    PeftTuning->>FS: Save prompt vectors<br/>(encoder/decoder artifacts)
    PeftTuning-->>gRPC: TrainingResult (model_id)
    gRPC-->>Client: TrainingResponse

    Note over Client,FS: Flow 4: Embedding Inference
    Client->>HTTP: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>HTTP / Configurable TLS
    HTTP->>EmbedMod: dispatch run()
    EmbedMod->>STModel: encode()<br/>(sentence-transformers)
    STModel-->>EmbedMod: Embedding vector(s)
    EmbedMod-->>HTTP: EmbeddingResult
    HTTP-->>Client: JSON Response
